text: Eunidia idactiformis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1954. It is known from Tanzania and Kenya.BioLib.cz - Eunidia idactiformis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1954
title: Eunidia idactiformis
